Interface IShallowParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbapShallowParser, AdaShallowParser, CobolShallowParser, CppShallowParser, CsShallowParser, CStyleShallowParserBase, DelphiShallowParser, FortranShallowParser, GoShallowParser, GosuShallowParser, GroovyShallowParser, HanaSQLScriptShallowParser, Iec61131ShallowParser, JavaScriptShallowParser, JavaShallowParser, KotlinShallowParser, LineShallowParser, MatlabShallowParser, ObjectiveCShallowParser, OcamlShallowParser, OpenCLShallowParser, OScriptShallowParser, PhpShallowParser, PlsqlShallowParser, PythonShallowParser, RubyShallowParser, RustShallowParser, ShallowParserBase, SwiftShallowParser, TsqlShallowParser, VisualBasicShallowParser, XtendShallowParser

    public interface IShallowParser
    Interface for a shallow parser. All shallow parsers are sufficiently robust to support parsing even of non-compiling code and arbitrary code snippets.

    • Method Detail

      • parseTopLevel

        java.util.List<ShallowEntity> parseTopLevel(java.util.List<IToken> tokens)
        Shallow parses the given list of tokens and returns all entities found. The tokens provided are expected to represent an entire top-level element of the language (typically a file).

      • parseFragment

        java.util.List<ShallowEntity> parseFragment(java.util.List<IToken> tokens)
        Shallow parses the given list of tokens and returns all entities found. The tokens provided may be from an arbitrary contiguous chunk of source code.
